data.payload:
{
  "channel": "{{local_var.channel_id}}",
  "blocks": [
    {
      "type": "header",
      "text": {
        "type": "plain_text",
        "emoji": true,
        "text": "DNS Tunneling / C2 Beaconing — Gateway DNS (HIGH)"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "section",
      "text": {
        "type": "mrkdwn",
        "text": "*A single source is tunneling data / beaconing to C2 over DNS via Cloudflare Gateway.*\n\n*Source IP:* `{{local_var.src_ip}}`  (geo: {{Function.DEFAULT(virustotal-search-ip.body.data.attributes.country, "N/A")}})\n*VirusTotal:* {{Function.DEFAULT(virustotal-search-ip.body.data.attributes.last_analysis_stats.malicious, "N/A")}} engines malicious\n*AbuseIPDB:* {{Function.DEFAULT(abuseipdb-check-ip.body.data.abuseConfidenceScore, "N/A")}}/100 abuse confidence\n*Suspected C2 domain:* `{{local_var.c2_domain}}`\n*DNS query volume (beaconing):* *{{local_var.total_queries}}*\n*Distinct subdomains:* {{local_var.distinct_subdomains}}  |  *Long labels:* {{local_var.long_subdomains}} (max len {{local_var.max_label_len}})\n*ATT&CK:* T1071.004 / T1048 / T1568.002"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "section",
      "text": {
        "type": "mrkdwn",
        "text": "*Before you block:* confirm `{{local_var.src_ip}}` is not a shared resolver/forwarder egress and the domain is not a legitimate high-cardinality cloud service (Azure/AWS/CDN). If it is, Dismiss."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "section",
      "text": {
        "type": "mrkdwn",
        "text": "*Alert:* <{{Function.GET_MANAGEMENT_URL()}}/incidents/unified-alerts?alertId={{singularity-response-trigger.data.id}}|{{singularity-response-trigger.data.name}}>"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "actions",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "button",
          "text": {
            "type": "plain_text",
            "emoji": true,
            "text": "Block at Cloudflare"
          },
          "style": "primary",
          "value": "approved"
        },
        {
          "type": "button",
          "text": {
            "type": "plain_text",
            "emoji": true,
            "text": "Dismiss — False Positive"
          },
          "style": "danger",
          "value": "dismissed"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "context",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "mrkdwn",
          "text": "⏳ *Please respond by {{Function.SUBSTRING(Function.STRING(Function.DELTA_NOW(-19)), 16)}} CT* — 24-hour SLA (US Central)."
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}

{
  "channel": "{{local_var.channel_id}}",
  "ts": "{{send-interactive-message.body.ts}}",
  "text": ":white_check_mark: `{{local_var.src_ip}}` was blocked at the Cloudflare edge (IP Access Rule) by {{wait-for-slack.body.user.username}}.\n\n*Alert:* <{{Function.GET_MANAGEMENT_URL()}}/incidents/unified-alerts?alertId={{singularity-response-trigger.data.id}}|{{singularity-response-trigger.data.name}}>"
}

{
  "channel": "{{local_var.channel_id}}",
  "ts": "{{send-interactive-message.body.ts}}",
  "text": ":x: Dismissed as false positive (e.g. shared corporate egress / NAT). No block applied. Alert: <{{Function.GET_MANAGEMENT_URL()}}/incidents/unified-alerts?alertId={{singularity-response-trigger.data.id}}|{{singularity-response-trigger.data.name}}>"
}
